{"tid":1524122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Popo新聞發表會流程流出","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:27:43.000Z","uid":50005,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bea596405fcd2e04a4cc3efb4854538df49883bc","tid":1524122,"uid":50005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"首先譴責暴徒 地鐵721事件<br />\n播片<br />\n講假新聞 講個警犬比人砍<br />\n用英文再講一次<br />\n到問答環節<br />\n問既全部都係左派黨媒<br />\n一定有大公報問佢塊mon <br />\n大陸記者問機場個條友 虛假新聞<br />\n之後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完</span></span> <br />\n企圖完全轉移<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際既視線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完你老母</span></span><br />\n香港記者你要保持中立完全可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">接受</span></span></span><br />\n但你地都唔可以唔問<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>維園粒子彈</strong>/red]</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[red]警犬佩帶警槍假扮示威者</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>地鐵屍殺列車</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被捕人實時情況</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警犬自編自導既砍人案</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新聞自由 大眾知情權比政府强行奪走</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一定要追住黎問 不畏<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">强權打壓</span></span></strong><br />\n即使話無資料答唔到 都要問到口啞 揭破<br />\n言荒 言!<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔係將自己對勇武派既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望<ins></ins></span></strong>轉移你地身上 先叫你地哥哥姐姐<br />\n而係香港人<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">相信</span></span></strong>你地既筆同嘴報道到真實而赤裸的事實比香港人 甚至<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際的朋友</span></span>聽<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上呀大眾利君雅</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9859ece750442675860e5d5b38fee020bff3b1","tid":1524122,"uid":50005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e2f5ae41293c9d4c3e157b4d363ce4fdb88631ea","tid":1524122,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"［文宣超新星爆炸］ 魔警阻止人道救援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMjHJNz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMjHJNz.jpg&h=3027d600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F125201912155933%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70p1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=fdd3aae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚唔人道 係咪可以推到班撚樣上軍事法庭<br />\nSorry P牌每日一post 有冇手足幫手開post"},{"pid":"94967bcec390275e8252cc0eaca6eaa499e20a37","tid":1524122,"uid":244809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"建議記者靜默抗議<br />\n唔駛問問題，市民有答案"},{"pid":"b937b8aec389fe43ba087f4da87ec8e16f141a0e","tid":1524122,"uid":55382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:45:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"796a9b7085bf4cfa34452659ca6f45eb56f89818","tid":1524122,"uid":93649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94967bcec390275e8252cc0eaca6eaa499e20a37","tid":1524122,"uid":244809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"建議記者靜默抗議<br />\